title: Abraham Lincoln Birthplace National Historical Park: People
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     History & Culture     People               People In The Early Life of Abraham Lincoln       The experiences of the early years in the life of Abraham Lincoln on the frontier of Kentucky instilled him with values that remained with him throughout his life.  You may learn more about Abraham Lincoln, his parents, and siblings by exploring the history and culture of Abraham Lincoln Birthplace National Historical Park.
